    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-08-31T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-08-31T00:00:00-05:00" n="69"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d69">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">724.3415/2188</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Commission of Neutrals</gloss> to the
                        Bolivian Minister for Foreign Affairs (<persName corresp="#p_GJA1" type="to"
                            >Gutiérrez</persName>)</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-08-31">August 31,
                            1932</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Commission of Neutrals has received with pleasure Your Excellency’s reply in
                    which you accept the suspension of hostilities for 30 days, and which it is
                    transmitting to Paraguay.</p>
                <p>The opportunity is taken to advise you, in reply to Your Excellency’s cablegram,
                    that the doctrine of August 3 does not have an exceptional character but is
                    applicable to this and to all other future cases.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_WF1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Francis White</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                    <lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">President of the Commission of Neutrals</hi>
                    <lb/>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_VAJ1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">J. Varela</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                    <lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister of Uruguay</hi>
                    <lb/>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LTF1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Fabio Lozano T.</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                    <lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister of Colombia</hi>
                    <lb/>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_BJT1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">José T. Barón</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                    <lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé d’Affaires of Cuba</hi>
                    <lb/>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_HHP1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">P. Herrera de Huerta</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                    <lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé d’Affaires of Mexico</hi>
                </closer>
            </div>
